05_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=e27F0QvBgaUQ7kNvgFlsDIY&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBNrME185cHFv6lcxu-93syiu2IU6Rknd7WMq4G-sXZAw&oe=66EA9F93"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Landscape_2560_1440_Oculus1.png", "id": "1138853546573929", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001717_1138853549907262_6485199567914041408_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=I3T36u6DzfoQ7kNvgGsEd__&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBZEaT81DRPK9E0uFDBTqyTem2XKQ-TrMct7sAWW4Y6Mg&oe=66EABBFB"}, "display_name": "Windlands", "keywords": [], "long_description": "A first-person grappling hook exploration game.\n\nSoar through the ruins of a fallen civilization and discover the secrets of the ancient world.\n\nIt appeals to those who want to explore the breathtaking vistas at a relaxing pace, while the challenging routes attract gamers who like to master the skill of soaring through the towering environments at top speed.\n\nGameplay Features\n\n* Designed and built for Virtual Reality First.\n* Grappling Hooks Focused Movement.\n* Variety of expansive levels that reward exploration.\n* Multiple routes provide a range of optional challenges.\n* Optional Skill based Speed Runs and Time Trials\n* Goal Driven Gameplay with Easy (Hook Anything), Normal and Hard Modes.", "short_description": "A first-person grappling hook exploration game. Soar through the ruins of a fallen civilization and discover the secrets of the ancient world."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.windlands.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.windlands.com/terms", "publisher_name": "Psytec Games Ltd", "support_website_url": "http://support.psytecgames.com/", "website_url": "http://www.windlands.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["